## Audit Checklist

### Story 5.1: Visualize Km Distribution
```typescript
// Playwright test:
await page.goto('/balancing');
await expect(page.locator('.histogram')).toBeVisible();
await expect(page.locator('.average-line')).toBeVisible();
```
- [ ] Histogram chart visible
- [ ] X-axis shows km ranges
- [ ] Y-axis shows train count
- [ ] Fleet average line marked
- [ ] Target range highlighted
- [ ] Interactive (hover shows count)

### Story 5.2: Rank Trains by Delta
```typescript
// Playwright test:
await page.goto('/balancing');
await expect(page.locator('table.rankings')).toBeVisible();
const rows = page.locator('table.rankings tbody tr');
await expect(rows).toHaveCount({ min: 10 });
```
- [ ] Rankings table visible
- [ ] Shows Train ID, Current km, Average, Delta
- [ ] Sorted by absolute delta
- [ ] Top 5 over-running highlighted
- [ ] Top 5 under-running highlighted

### Story 5.3: Identify Outliers
```typescript
// Playwright test:
await page.goto('/balancing');
await expect(page.locator('.outliers-panel')).toBeVisible();
```
- [ ] Outliers panel visible
- [ ] Shows trains >15% deviation
- [ ] Different color in histogram
- [ ] Recommendations shown

